        "type": "practiceLevel1",
        "lessons": [
          {
            "title": "Intro",
            "id": 126872,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Jusqu'à présent, nous avons appris à créer une boucle while, concentrons-nous maintenant sur la façon de les empêcher de boucler indéfiniment.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"...\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Looks like your code runs forever. It may be that an infinite loop exists in your code.\" /></content></output></code></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Creating the variable",
            "id": 126873,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Pour arrêter une boucle, nous commençons par créer une variable en dehors de la boucle.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepGoing = \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"3\" /><option startIndex=\"4\" endIndex=\"13\" /><option startIndex=\"14\" endIndex=\"15\" /><option startIndex=\"16\" endIndex=\"20\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"...\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Looks like your code runs forever. It may be that an infinite loop exists in your code.\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de choisir <code>let</code> suivi de <code>keepGoing</code> puis <code>=</code>, <code>true</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Variable in the condition",
            "id": 126874,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Nous utilisons la variable dans la condition pour décider si la boucle doit exécuter son bloc de code ou non. Par exemple, <code>while keepGoing</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepGoing = \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepGoing {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"27\" endIndex=\"36\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"...\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Looks like your code runs forever. It may be that an infinite loop exists in your code.\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de choisir <code>keepGoing</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Updating the variable",
            "id": 126875,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>À l'intérieur du bloc de code, nous arrêtons la boucle en définissant <code>keepGoing</code> sur <code>false</code> afin que la condition renvoie <code>false</code>.</p><code name=\"main.swift\" version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepGoing = \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepGoing {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" keepGoing = \" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"true\" /></content></option><option startIndex=\"72\" endIndex=\"77\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de choisir <code>false</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Stopping the loop",
            "id": 126876,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>La boucle exécute l'intégralité de son bloc de code parce que <code>keepGoing</code> est <code>true</code> au début, mais ne s'exécute pas à nouveau si nous définissons <code>keepGoing</code> à <code>false</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepGoing = \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepGoing {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;keepGoing: \\(keepGoing)&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" keepGoing = \" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;keepGoing: \\(keepGoing)&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"87\" endIndex=\"92\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"keepGoing: true\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"keepGoing: false\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de rentrer <code>false</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Creating the variable",
            "id": 126877,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Comment savons-nous que cette boucle s'exécute et ne cesse jamais de répéter son bloc de code ?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" isLoading = \" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Loading Game&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"Loading Game\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Loading Game\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Loading Game\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"...\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Looks like your code runs forever. It may be that an infinite loop exists in your code.\" /></content></output></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">Il n'y a pas de variable dans la condition</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">Cette boucle ne s'exécutera pas car la condition est <code>false</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Il n'y a pas de variable dans la condition.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Variable in the condition",
            "id": 126878,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Comment savons-nous que la boucle <code>while</code> saute son bloc de code ?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" isLoading = \" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" isLoading {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Loading Game&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">La valeur de <code>isLoading</code> est <code>false</code> mais la condition vérifie si elle est <code>true</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">La valeur de <code>isLoading</code> est <code>false</code> et la condition vérifie si elle est <code>false</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">La valeur de <code>isLoading</code> est <code>false</code> mais la condition vérifie si elle est <code>true</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Updating the variable",
            "id": 126879,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Comment savons-nous que cette boucle s'arrête ?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepGoing = \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepGoing {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Just keep swimming&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" keepGoing = \" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"Just keep swimming\" /></content></output></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">La variable <code>keepGoing</code> se met à jour à <code>false</code> à l'intérieur du bloc de code</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">Nous ne savons pas si la boucle s'arrête</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">La variable <code>keepGoing</code> se met à jour à <code>false</code> à l'intérieur du bloc de code.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
