            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Que montre ce code dans la console ?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepPlaying = \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" keepPlaying {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Now Playing: Dolce Vita&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" keepPlaying = \" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"Now Playing: Dolce Vita\" /></content></output></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\"><code>Now Playing: Dolce Vita</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">Ce code n'affiche rien dans la console</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\"><code>Now Playing: Dolce Vita</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
